{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b2df15f1ec","title":"浪淘沙·北戴河","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3d5ddabb8a","index":0,"year":1954,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"b2df15f1ec"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"51a1c507a3","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b2df15f1ec","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"北戴河，在河北省东北部潮海边港口秦皇岛西，是著名夏季休养地。"},{"id":"d78f3430b1","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b2df15f1ec","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"幽燕，泛指河北省。我国古代的幽州和燕国，都在今河北省北部一带。"},{"id":"ba51052698","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b2df15f1ec","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"往事越千年，魏武挥鞭，东临码石有遗篇。公元207年（汉献帝建安十二年），曹操（后被尊称魏武帝）和乌恒族作战凯旋，曾经路过这一带。曹操的《步出夏门行》诗中有《观沧海》一章：“东临码石（据近年来考古发现，码石在今辽宁省绥中县西南的海滨，西距山海关约30里），以观沧海。......秋风萧瑟，洪波涌起。…...."}],"contents":[{"id":"63edfd336d","type":"title","text":"浪淘沙·北戴河","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b2df15f1ec"},{"id":"51a1c507a3","type":"paragraph","text":"大雨落幽燕以白浪涵天，秦皇岛外打鱼船。一片汪洋都不见，知向谁边？往事越千年，魏武挥鞭，东临码石有遗篇。国]萧瑟秋风今又是，换了人间。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b2df15f1ec"}],"page":{"id":"309d151eb2","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b2df15f1ec","start":180,"end":180}}}},"__N_SSG":true}